Anyway, in my opinion, they're completely different.

32
00:03:00,959 --> 00:03:04,679
Maybe you've seen Physician Bian before?

33
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,559
I don't think so.

34
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:16,099
Miss Yue, have you ever heard of Rehai before?

35
00:03:18,459 --> 00:03:22,400
 The matter of Rehai is confidential. Don't tell anyone. 

36
00:03:31,999 --> 00:03:37,360
Then, Miss Yue, is there anything special about you?

37
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:40,799
I'm especially smart and clever, does that count?

38
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:44,480
Anything else?

39
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,959
Then, no.

40
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:53,319
Trust among friends. This is the last time I'll ask.

41
00:03:53,319 --> 00:03:55,800
But I have one more favor to ask.

42
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:58,999
Can you not tell anyone that I asked you those questions?

43
00:03:58,999 --> 00:04:00,760
Why?

44
00:04:02,279 --> 00:04:04,239
This is important to me.

45
00:04:04,239 --> 00:04:07,340
So please keep it a secret and don't tell anyone else.

46
00:04:07,340 --> 00:04:08,899
All right, I promise you.

47
00:04:08,899 --> 00:04:13,559
Zhaoyan, you've been good to us. As long as Jinzhao doesn't ask, I won't tell him.

48
00:04:15,559 --> 00:04:20,440
But even if Brother Yue asks, don't tell him. Is that okay?

49
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:25,279
No way. If Jinzhao asks me, I'll definitely tell him.

50
00:04:28,980 --> 00:04:30,819
- Well... 
 - Sorry.

51
00:04:30,819 --> 00:04:33,620
The villagers had some medical questions and I was delayed.

52
00:04:33,620 --> 00:04:35,720
Is there anything wrong with the patient?

53
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:38,800
No.

54
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:47,299
Zhaoyan, what's wrong with you?

55
00:04:47,299 --> 00:04:49,199
Let me check.

56
00:04:50,039 --> 00:04:52,739
Don't bother, Physician Bian. It's just an old illness.

57
00:04:52,739 --> 00:04:56,199
Master Luo doesn't trust my medical skills?

58
00:04:57,520 --> 00:05:01,440
Zhaoyan, you should let Physician Bian check you.

59
00:05:07,119 --> 00:05:09,160
Then please, Physician Bian.

60
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:18,960
You seem to be in a condition I've never seen before.

61
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:23,999
It's okay. I just need to rest for a while. Thank you.

62
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:36,520
I'm fine.

63
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:38,939
 There are no physical abnormalities, 

64
00:05:38,939 --> 00:05:42,720
 yet the life force is flowing out of the body. 

65
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:47,300
 Is it the curse of the Twilight Luo family's twins dying young? 

66
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:49,720
No more nagging from now on.

67
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,360
I'm telling you. You all heard it.

68
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:55,380
Physician Bian said everything would be clear when that patient wakes up.

69
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:57,099
Don't be so timid all the time.

70
00:05:57,099 --> 00:05:59,099
Even if you don't trust him, you have to trust me. Right?

71
00:05:59,099 --> 00:06:00,459
Even if you don't trust him, you have to trust me. Right?

72
00:06:00,459 --> 00:06:02,620
Besides, with me here, there's nothing to worry about.

73
00:06:02,620 --> 00:06:06,240
Everything's ready. We just need to wait for the fish to bite.

74
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:08,080
Jinzhao, will this really work?

75
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:12,299
Of course. The wounded man attracted their attention already.

76
00:06:12,299 --> 00:06:16,719
To cover up the crime, they'll take action.

77
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:19,639
Miss Ming. Senior Xian Qing.

78
00:06:19,639 --> 00:06:22,000
You're done with your stroll?

79
00:06:22,919 --> 00:06:26,400
Yes. I'm getting old. It helps with digestion.

80
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:30,039
We've already found a place to stay. Let's pick up Brother Luo and Qi.

81
00:06:35,919 --> 00:06:39,140
Look! I drew a map of the whole village.

82
00:06:39,140 --> 00:06:42,030
What's... this?

83
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,939
The triangles represent houses.

84
00:06:44,939 --> 00:06:47,759
The circles represent caves.

85
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:52,560
So where are we now?

86
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:55,280
This is our current location.

87
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:58,360
This is Physician Bian's house. Right?

88
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:00,159
Yes, correct.

89
00:07:00,159 --> 00:07:03,719
Shifang, your map is really easy to understand.

90
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:11,140
Okay, then we'll hide near Bian Luohuan's house.

91
00:07:11,140 --> 00:07:14,520
Wait for them to take action, and then we can surround them.

92
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:17,360
Brother Yue, I wouldn't recommend catching them in the village.

93
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:20,680
It's dangerous. I'm afraid villagers might get hurt, that would be bad.

94
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:22,800
Then let's drive them to Linyang Road.

95
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:27,459
Brother Luo, Shifang, and Senior Xian Qing, you'll be waiting for the prey there.

96
00:07:27,459 --> 00:07:31,580
Qi, me, and Miss Ming, we'll keep watch near Bian Luohuan's house.

97
00:07:31,580 --> 00:07:32,680
Okay.

98
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,560
I'll stay to protect Physician Bian.

99
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,240
No way.

100
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:43,719
Well, I mean...

101
00:07:43,719 --> 00:07:45,199
Are you sure?

102
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:46,960
Yeah.

103
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:55,539
Jinzhao, you don't seem to want me to stay and protect Physician Bian.

104
00:07:55,539 --> 00:08:00,700
Not at all. I just wonder if you can do it or not.

105
00:08:00,700 --> 00:08:03,360
If I can't, can you?

106
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:08,879
Since it's all set up, let's go back and get some rest.

107
00:08:10,619 --> 00:08:12,240
Okay.

108
00:08:55,780 --> 00:08:59,332
 Physician Bian, have we met before? 

109
00:08:59,332 --> 00:09:01,199
 Perhaps. 

110
00:09:05,539 --> 00:09:09,180
Thinking about Qi is enough,

111
00:09:09,180 --> 00:09:13,240
but why is this Bian Luohuan getting into my head, too?

112
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:17,360
It's really weird.

113
00:09:23,020 --> 00:09:25,020
Jinzhao, do you have water?

114
00:09:25,020 --> 00:09:27,400
I'm in a medicated bath.

115
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,599
Close your eyes!

116
00:09:29,599 --> 00:09:31,300
Then, why didn't you shut the door?

117
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:33,560
Then, why didn't you knock?

118
00:09:34,900 --> 00:09:36,759
Don't open your eyes.

119
00:10:02,852 --> 00:10:06,792
♫  Looking back upon the past  ♫

120
00:10:06,792 --> 00:10:10,039
♫  Searching for that moment from the past  ♫

121
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:12,159
Are you thirsty, too?

122
00:10:14,852 --> 00:10:18,240
♫  It is destined to be  ♫

123
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:21,960
Qi, go outside first.

124
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:25,460
Why? You're dressed, aren't you?

125
00:10:25,460 --> 00:10:29,599
Do you have any water? I'm really thirsty.

126
00:10:29,599 --> 00:10:32,839
Knock on the door before you enter someone's room.

127
00:10:32,839 --> 00:10:35,159
You aren't just someone.

128
00:10:37,604 --> 00:10:41,572
♫  All my life's unforgettable moments are because of you  ♫

129
00:10:41,572 --> 00:10:43,204
♫  The past glides by scene by scene  ♫

130
00:10:43,204 --> 00:10:45,079
♫  How many smiles and tears  ♫

131
00:10:45,079 --> 00:10:50,240
Jinzhao, you're like a young lady like this.

132
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,299
Really.

133
00:10:51,299 --> 00:10:56,939
You're exactly like those young ladies I read in storybooks when they've been seen bathing.

134
00:10:56,939 --> 00:11:02,359
When they are seen, they are either outraged or embarrassed.

135
00:11:03,140 --> 00:11:07,076
Look! Look! Embarrassed, right?

136
00:11:07,076 --> 00:11:10,479
♫  Never forgetting this, I keep bitterly searching  ♫

137
00:11:10,479 --> 00:11:12,000
Jinzhao!

138
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:15,088
You got me wet. I'm not playing with you anymore.

139
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:17,156
♫  Among the vast sea of people, I engrave your name  ♫

140
00:11:17,156 --> 00:11:19,368
♫  Among the vast sea of people, I engrave your name  ♫

141
00:11:19,368 --> 00:11:26,768
♫  Never doubt, the steadfastness of my heart  ♫

142
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:34,140
Qi.

143
00:11:35,370 --> 00:11:39,970
Would you wipe someone else's head like this?

144
00:11:41,340 --> 00:11:43,184
No.

145
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,859
Why?

146
00:11:47,020 --> 00:11:51,000
Because Zhaoyan has a younger sister,

147
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,680
Shifang has Dou Bao,

148
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:56,079
and Ming Xiu has Xian Qing.

149
00:11:56,079 --> 00:12:00,700
It's a pity, you have no one else, so there's only me.

150
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:03,480
I'm not pitiful at all.

151
00:12:04,070 --> 00:12:05,980
I still have myself.

152
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:12,399
What a young lady.

153
00:12:12,399 --> 00:12:15,000
Shut up.

154
00:12:16,140 --> 00:12:19,380
Here's the water. Drink up.

155
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:27,120
Feels so nice.

156
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,340
Here.

157
00:12:28,340 --> 00:12:32,159
Qi, why do you love drinking water so much?

158
00:12:32,159 --> 00:12:34,599
Jinzhao, can you weave a straw butterfly?

159
00:12:34,599 --> 00:12:38,399
No. Why do you ask?

160
00:12:38,399 --> 00:12:41,599
In Physician Bian's cottage, there are many beautiful woven straw butterflies.

161
00:12:41,599 --> 00:12:43,939
I want one, too.

162
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:48,760
What man would like things that only girls make?

163
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:51,239
Then I'll ask Physician Bian for one.

164
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:57,939
Since when did you get so close to Physician Bian?

165
00:12:57,939 --> 00:13:01,560
Didn't I tell you many times not to talk to strangers?

166
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:03,519
I've always been close to him.

167
00:13:03,519 --> 00:13:06,700
I think Physician Bian feels very much like how you make me feel.

168
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:09,519
So I find him approachable.

169
00:13:15,839 --> 00:13:18,116
Jinzhao, what's the matter?

170
00:13:21,039 --> 00:13:22,880
Nothing.

171
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:26,460
By the way, when you were guarding Physician Bian's house,

172
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:28,760
did you notice anything weird?

173
00:13:29,970 --> 00:13:31,739
Do you mean Physician Bian or Zhaoyan?

174
00:13:31,739 --> 00:13:33,399
Physician Bian.

175
00:13:34,039 --> 00:13:35,610
What about Zhaoyan?

176
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:38,360
- Yes. 
 - What is it?

177
00:13:38,959 --> 00:13:43,479
He apologized to me. He said, "We're friends from now on."

178
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:51,360
Then he's quite clever, much better than his younger sister.

179
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:55,079
He also asked me if I knew about Rehai.

180
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:58,160
Rehai?

181
00:13:58,724 --> 00:14:00,552
   

182
00:14:02,479 --> 00:14:04,179
How did you answer?

183
00:14:04,179 --> 00:14:06,159
You told me to keep it a secret,

184
00:14:06,159 --> 00:14:08,360
so I said I didn't know.

185
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:13,159
However, Zhaoyan also told me to keep it a secret.

186
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:18,300
Zhaoyan asked you to keep it a secret. Why did you tell me then?

187
00:14:18,300 --> 00:14:21,079
I promised him I wouldn't tell you if you didn't ask.

188
00:14:21,079 --> 00:14:24,240
But since you've asked, I can't lie to you.

189
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:26,079
Good.

190
00:14:26,079 --> 00:14:28,079
Here, have some water.

191
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:39,039
Young Zhaoyan, are you enjoying the beautiful scenery?

192
00:14:39,039 --> 00:14:40,560
Senior.

193
00:14:41,930 --> 00:14:43,640
Not really.

194
00:14:46,680 --> 00:14:50,440
So you're concerned about tonight's operation.

195
00:14:54,020 --> 00:14:55,579
We have limited manpower.

196
00:14:55,579 --> 00:14:57,599
If tonight's operation fails,

197
00:14:57,599 --> 00:15:01,959
Physician Bian and that patient might both be in danger.

198
00:15:01,959 --> 00:15:06,240
Didn't you agree to the plan to lure the snake out?

199
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:11,680
If it's something you decided on, and you hesitate partway...

200
00:15:12,490 --> 00:15:16,200
Young Zhaoyan, this is what a hypocrite would do.

201
00:15:20,079 --> 00:15:25,000
What you said is very similar to what one of my family members said.

202
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:31,079
Perhaps, like he said, I really am a hypocrite.

203
00:15:34,656 --> 00:15:37,550
It's been a long time since I've seen someone so innocent.

204
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:40,341
You're funny and adorable.

205
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:44,440
A-Adorable?

206
00:15:46,039 --> 00:15:50,819
Senior, adorable isn't a word to describe me.

207
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:16,680
Today, we must not lose against Qiyuan Sect!

208
00:16:16,680 --> 00:16:18,479
Of course not!

209
00:16:18,479 --> 00:16:20,000
Let's go!

210
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:45,839
 Brother Luo, I'm going to need you to wait with me tonight. 

211
00:16:46,719 --> 00:16:51,280
 Miss Ming, Senior, and Shifang, you three ambush at Linyang Road. 

212
00:16:51,280 --> 00:16:55,410
 After Brother Luo and I lure them over, you can come out to fight. 

213
00:16:56,079 --> 00:17:00,580
 Qi, you keep an eye on Bian Luohuan and come to us if you get a chance. 

214
00:17:00,580 --> 00:17:03,839
 If you encounter a strong opponent on the way, don't try to be brave. 

215
00:17:03,839 --> 00:17:05,919
 Run if you can't win. 

216
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:16,039
We've been waiting a long time for you.

217
00:17:16,039 --> 00:17:17,839
Surround them!

218
00:17:19,730 --> 00:17:21,710
It's a trap! Retreat!

219
00:17:22,290 --> 00:17:23,680
Qi!

220
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:25,424
I'll protect this place.

221
00:17:33,260 --> 00:17:35,680
 Why am I suddenly so sleepy? 

222
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:39,208
 Why can't I open my eyes? 

223
00:18:10,320 --> 00:18:14,479
Stinky Jinzhao... stealing my eggs again.

224
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:02,520
There's demons.

225
00:19:13,559 --> 00:19:15,679
How dare you run wild here!

226
00:19:20,719 --> 00:19:22,599
Miss Ming, no!

227
00:19:23,730 --> 00:19:26,990
Hall Leader Ju, you know this demon? Why are you helping her?

228
00:19:27,590 --> 00:19:29,799
Miss Shuo Xuan is a demon?

229
00:19:51,319 --> 00:19:53,679
Come on, keep running.

230
00:19:55,760 --> 00:19:57,199
Where's Shifang?

231
00:19:57,199 --> 00:19:59,499
Young Shifang was captured by a demon.

232
00:19:59,499 --> 00:20:01,080
I'll go take a look.

233
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:05,920
Wait!

234
00:20:06,679 --> 00:20:08,400
Miss Shuo Xuan,

235
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:12,339
are you... a good demon or a bad one?

236
00:20:12,339 --> 00:20:14,719
Garbage doesn't deserve to know.

237
00:20:14,719 --> 00:20:16,619
I'm not garbage.

238
00:20:16,619 --> 00:20:20,079
I just don't want to fight you.

239
00:20:23,479 --> 00:20:27,900
Miss Shuo Xuan, do you want to kill me?

240
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:32,020
Killing an ant isn't something I need to do personally.

241
00:20:32,020 --> 00:20:37,920
D-Do you really have something to do with the Qiyuan Sect?

242
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:42,280
Qiyuan Sect is just a small sect. I really don't care.

243
00:20:42,280 --> 00:20:45,280
You've been tricked into harming innocent people by the Qiyuan Sect.

244
00:20:45,280 --> 00:20:49,199
Drop your weapons and tell us who's behind it, so you can make amends.

245
00:20:49,199 --> 00:20:50,880
Harming innocent people?

246
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:54,140
How dare you ruin the reputation of the Qiyuan Sect!

247
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:55,420
Stubborn.

248
00:20:55,420 --> 00:20:57,760
Brothers, attack!

249
00:21:19,060 --> 00:21:21,099
It's you!

250
00:21:21,099 --> 00:21:23,320
Miss Shuo Xuan,

251
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:27,199
if one day, you and I become enemies,

252
00:21:27,199 --> 00:21:32,059
I-I'll definitely beat you and lead you onto the right path.

253
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:37,559
You really are such a dreamer.

