00:21:37,559 --> 00:21:42,719
Just with those shoddy gadgets? Against me?

255
00:21:43,479 --> 00:21:45,099
Are you worthy?

256
00:21:45,099 --> 00:21:46,719
One more thing,

257
00:21:48,120 --> 00:21:49,920
