261
00:22:03,799 --> 00:22:05,360
 Shifang! 

262
00:22:10,780 --> 00:22:13,640
How are you? Are you okay?

263
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:16,040
I'm okay. Miss Shuo Xuan didn't hurt me.

264
00:22:16,040 --> 00:22:18,000
Shuo Xuan?

265
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:19,679
She's a demon?

266
00:22:20,799 --> 00:22:22,759
