267
00:22:24,300 --> 00:22:26,479
Last time, she paid particular attention to Qi.

268
00:22:26,479 --> 00:22:28,040
Now it's her again.

269
00:22:28,040 --> 00:22:31,079
Next time I see her, I have to ask her.

270
00:22:31,079 --> 00:22:33,499
Come... let's go find Brother Luo.

271
00:22:36,320 --> 00:22:38,439
Oh no. We've been exposed!

272
00:22:38,439 --> 00:22:41,679
That person will kill us. Let's just be honest.

273
00:22:50,439 --> 00:22:52,199
Leave him alive!

274
00:22:58,559 --> 00:23:00,959
May Lord Ming bless us.

275
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:32,100
I'm responsible for keeping an eye on Qi and Yue Jinzhao, not you.

276
00:23:32,799 --> 00:23:35,360
Do you think I want to do this?

277
00:23:37,120 --> 00:23:39,159
You exposed yourself at Jincui Oasis,

278
00:23:39,159 --> 00:23:41,610
it's already aroused Yue Jinzhao's suspicions.

279
00:23:42,240 --> 00:23:44,360
If you interfere again,

280
00:23:45,050 --> 00:23:47,519
I won't show you any mercy.

281
00:24:24,810 --> 00:24:27,120
Why did I fall asleep?

282
00:24:30,170 --> 00:24:31,779
Physician Bian.

283
00:24:31,779 --> 00:24:35,140
Physician Bian, let me check.

284
00:24:35,140 --> 00:24:37,000
Are you okay?

285
00:24:40,340 --> 00:24:42,059
Good then.

286
00:24:42,059 --> 00:24:43,740
What about him?

287
00:24:44,340 --> 00:24:46,159
He'll wake up soon.

288
00:24:47,570 --> 00:24:50,879
What about Jinzhao? Why aren't they back yet?

289
00:24:53,930 --> 00:24:56,620
Are they in some kind of danger?

290
00:24:56,620 --> 00:25:00,539
As expected, he can't do it without my protection.

291
00:25:00,539 --> 00:25:02,759
What an idiot.

292
00:25:03,919 --> 00:25:05,120
 Pathetic. 

293
00:25:05,120 --> 00:25:07,279
 Why is someone dead? 

294
00:25:07,279 --> 00:25:09,240
 What happened? 

295
00:25:12,300 --> 00:25:13,940
Jinzhao, are you okay?

296
00:25:13,940 --> 00:25:16,979
How could I get injured so easily? Come on.

297
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:20,000
Zhuo'er. Zhuo'er.

298
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:22,280
Zhuo'er!

299
00:25:26,180 --> 00:25:29,659
My son!

300
00:25:32,850 --> 00:25:36,640
Shifang, you don't look so well. Have you been injured?

301
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:38,120
No.

302
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:41,390
I just saw... so many people die.

303
00:25:42,079 --> 00:25:44,479
I just wanted to catch them,

304
00:25:44,479 --> 00:25:47,459
but I didn't expect I would drive them to death.

305
00:25:47,459 --> 00:25:49,280
I caused them to die.

306
00:25:49,280 --> 00:25:53,360
Hall Leader Ju, as the head of the Righteous Martial Alliance, you should kill demons and evils.

307
00:25:53,360 --> 00:25:55,599
Yet you fear this?

308
00:25:55,599 --> 00:25:58,599
I'm not. But...

309
00:25:58,599 --> 00:26:01,779
But they were all living beings.

310
00:26:04,439 --> 00:26:07,279
It's you all who caused them to die!

311
00:26:07,279 --> 00:26:10,579
 - It's them. Definitely them. 
 - Right, it must be them. 

312
00:26:10,579 --> 00:26:13,020
 I knew it. It's them. 

313
00:26:13,020 --> 00:26:15,119
 - It's them. 
 - It's them. 

314
00:26:15,799 --> 00:26:18,240
You wicked people!

315
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:22,640
They had it coming. You dare blame us?

316
00:26:22,640 --> 00:26:26,320
Weren't you here to hurt us anyway?!

317
00:26:26,320 --> 00:26:29,724
 - Exactly! 
 - They're here to hurt us! 

318
00:26:29,724 --> 00:26:32,080
Sir, please hear me out.

319
00:26:32,080 --> 00:26:35,900
We came here because we knew this might be the stronghold of the Qiyuan Sect.

320
00:26:35,900 --> 00:26:38,520
And the people who died were from the Qiyuan Sect.

321
00:26:38,520 --> 00:26:40,619
So they deserved to die?!

322
00:26:40,619 --> 00:26:43,679
No, we were trying to lure them out and capture them,

323
00:26:43,679 --> 00:26:45,880
but unexpectedly, they all killed themselves.

324
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:49,379
Perhaps we should go check their houses together to look for any clues.

325
00:26:49,379 --> 00:26:54,280
Brother Yue, there's no need to explain. This was caused by me.

326
00:26:54,280 --> 00:26:57,020
It's my fault. I didn't stop them from killing themselves.

327
00:26:57,020 --> 00:27:01,479
Everyone, I'm willing to bear all your grief and anger.

328
00:27:01,479 --> 00:27:04,599
You'll bear it? You'll bear it?!

329
00:27:04,599 --> 00:27:06,940
Can you bring them back to life?!

330
00:27:06,940 --> 00:27:08,959
 Yeah, can you bring them back to life? 

331
00:27:08,959 --> 00:27:11,559
 Can you bring them back to life? 

332
00:27:11,559 --> 00:27:14,519
 - Right. 
 - He only knows how to talk! 

333
00:27:15,280 --> 00:27:18,640
Young Zhaoyan, there's no need to talk to them anymore.

334
00:27:19,479 --> 00:27:21,120
Everyone,

335
00:27:22,199 --> 00:27:27,079
I suppose you're the heroes who saved me.

336
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:30,959
Why are you outside? Are you okay?

337
00:27:30,959 --> 00:27:32,980
I'm much better now.

338
00:27:32,980 --> 00:27:37,120
If you don't clarify the situation soon, the heroes will be in danger.

339
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:42,399
Everyone, listen to me. My name is Lang Mo.

340
00:27:42,399 --> 00:27:46,499
I'm a businessman who came from Mangwan Village to Yinghui Fort.

341
00:27:48,120 --> 00:27:53,039
People from the Qiyuan Sect knocked me out and then locked me up.

342
00:27:54,479 --> 00:27:58,559
There were a lot of other people locked up with me.

343
00:27:59,420 --> 00:28:00,680
It was them!

344
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:02,479
Impossible.

345
00:28:03,120 --> 00:28:06,512
- Impossible... 
 - I wonder what happened to the others.

346
00:28:07,490 --> 00:28:12,010
Heroes, please go save them.

347
00:28:12,010 --> 00:28:14,559
Are you telling the truth?

348
00:28:15,510 --> 00:28:17,620
I'll bet my life on it.

349
00:28:18,240 --> 00:28:20,060
 It seems to be true. 

350
00:28:20,060 --> 00:28:22,099
 - Yes. 
 - Really. 

351
00:28:22,099 --> 00:28:24,320
 - It seems to be true.  
 - Fine.

352
00:28:25,030 --> 00:28:26,920
So be it.

353
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:33,679
I'll let you... take a look at Zhuo'er's room.

354
00:28:33,679 --> 00:28:35,160
Let's go.

355
00:28:35,959 --> 00:28:38,240
 - Go, take a look. 
 - Let's take a look. 

356
00:28:38,240 --> 00:28:39,760
 We'll know what's real and what's not then. 

357
00:28:39,760 --> 00:28:40,959
 Just take a look. 

358
00:28:40,959 --> 00:28:42,640
Are you okay?

359
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:46,679
Lang Mo, I'll take you to the cottage.

360
00:28:46,679 --> 00:28:50,839
I can go back myself. Master Luo, you go ahead.

361
00:29:23,610 --> 00:29:27,360
Oh my! There's a secret chamber.

362
00:29:44,900 --> 00:29:48,839
Jinzhao, do you think there might be a Qiyuan Orb here too?

363
00:30:05,080 --> 00:30:08,479
Young Xiu, what is this?

364
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:18,799
This is the enchanting herb. It can be refined into enchanting drug.

365
00:30:20,319 --> 00:30:24,760
I remember we found this herb in Fujin Hall.

366
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:29,019
It seems that Qiyuan Sect's enchanting drug is made from this herb.

367
00:30:29,019 --> 00:30:34,259
Although the scent is weak, Bian Luohuan's house does have this scent.

368
00:30:35,420 --> 00:30:36,619
You mean...

369
00:30:36,619 --> 00:30:41,679
Unless someone touched it, it's hard for the scent to stay on someone.

370
00:30:41,679 --> 00:30:46,380
Also, I've never heard of such herbs growing in the Western Regions.

371
00:30:46,380 --> 00:30:50,760
Qi, was there anything wrong with Bian Luohuan last night?

372
00:30:55,920 --> 00:31:00,679
Last night, I fell asleep in Physician Bian's cottage.

373
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:05,320
So you wouldn't know what he did.

374
00:31:07,079 --> 00:31:10,959
Do you think Bian Luohuan deliberately made Miss Yue fall asleep?

375
00:31:11,770 --> 00:31:14,499
Young Yue, come up.

376
00:31:24,810 --> 00:31:27,040
Young Yue has been in the cottage for too long.

377
00:31:27,040 --> 00:31:31,161
There're dozens of scents on her. I can't tell the specific one.

378
00:31:33,210 --> 00:31:36,640
Well... could it be we're overthinking it?

379
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:39,679
Maybe Young Yue was just too tired.

380
00:31:39,679 --> 00:31:41,859
I don't think Physician Bian is a bad person.

381
00:31:41,859 --> 00:31:43,840
He even helped us save Lang Mo.

382
00:31:43,840 --> 00:31:47,080
Those disciples said something very interesting before they died.

383
00:31:47,080 --> 00:31:49,280
"That person will kill us."

384
00:31:50,479 --> 00:31:54,240
It means the one behind them is in Luori Village right now.

385
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:56,959
And Bian Luohuan is really suspicious.

386
00:31:56,959 --> 00:31:58,679
We can never be too careful.

387
00:31:58,679 --> 00:32:02,040
Just pretend we don't know anything, and observe some more.

388
00:32:23,420 --> 00:32:25,599
Hurry, go get Physician Bian!

389
00:32:25,599 --> 00:32:27,280
Quick!

390
00:32:37,079 --> 00:32:39,280
