412
00:35:30,520 --> 00:35:34,719
If something happens to her, I will never let you off.

413
00:35:34,719 --> 00:35:36,959
I don't want anything to happen to her either.

414
00:35:43,799 --> 00:35:47,199
Qi. Qi.

415
00:35:48,450 --> 00:35:50,410
I want some water.

416
00:35:51,040 --> 00:35:54,000
You all go rest. I'll take care of Qi.

417
00:35:54,839 --> 00:35:58,480
Th-Then we'll leave now.

418
00:36:02,240 --> 00:36:03,700
Qi.

419
00:36:05,120 --> 00:36:08,380
- Water. 
 - Water.

